Ken wasn't supposed
to be here.

00:08.274 --> 00:11.011
It's like he just
stumbled on the abduction.

00:11.044 --> 00:12.846
And Josh is supposed
to be the next victim.

00:12.879 --> 00:14.047
Neil:
Say hi to Daddy.

00:14.080 --> 00:16.216
Kular:
This is Neil Cuthbert.

00:16.249 --> 00:18.752
Detained in Quebec after a
suspected contract killing.

00:18.785 --> 00:19.753
(grunt)

00:19.786 --> 00:20.754
(gun shot)
(moans)

00:20.787 --> 00:21.755
Cardinal:
That's our suspect.

00:21.788 --> 00:22.756
Ken:
Scott.

00:22.789 --> 00:23.757
Where's my son?

00:23.790 --> 00:25.125
You said you could
keep me safe.

00:25.158 --> 00:26.960
(dramatic instrumental)

00:26.993 --> 00:28.428
(boom)

00:28.461 --> 00:29.629
(sirens wailing)

00:29.662 --> 00:30.964
(pulsing suspenseful music)

00:30.997 --> 00:32.098
He's alive!

00:32.132 --> 00:34.267
The doctors say
Josh will be okay.

00:34.300 --> 00:35.268
With Neil Cuthbert dead,

00:35.301 --> 00:36.269
do we think the
killings will stop?

00:36.302 --> 00:37.270
(pulsing suspenseful music)

00:37.303 --> 00:38.271
(dramatic beat)

00:38.304 --> 00:39.539
No, they won't stop.

00:39.572 --> 00:41.307
(pensive orchestral music)

00:41.341 --> 00:45.378
("Familiar" by Agnes Obel)

00:45.412 --> 00:49.149
♪ Took a walk to
