09:17.123 --> 09:18.357
Aagimaak used to be huge.

09:18.391 --> 09:20.927
It was thousands of
acres of crown land.

09:20.960 --> 09:23.796
It's mostly been divided
up and sold off.

09:23.829 --> 09:26.065
Okay, let's put some satellite
pictures on the monitor.

09:26.098 --> 09:29.035
Maybe you can try to figure out
where he might've taken Ken.

09:29.068 --> 09:30.803
He's chosen a clear cut,

09:30.836 --> 09:34.407
a salvage yard
and a quarry.

09:34.440 --> 09:35.741
Well, Ken McNider

09:35.775 --> 09:38.377
had sawmills and quarries
running all over the area.

09:38.411 --> 09:39.946
Start with those.

