18:27.973 --> 18:29.675
I can't do this
right now, Kel,

18:29.708 --> 18:32.244
but stay and we'll
talk later, okay?

18:32.277 --> 18:34.613
No no, it's okay, um,

18:34.646 --> 18:36.849
I'm sorry, I shouldn't
have surprised you.

18:36.882 --> 18:37.850
I'll head back.

18:37.883 --> 18:40.552
No, no, please.

18:44.089 --> 18:45.090
I'm sorry.

18:46.925 --> 18:49.995
Kel, I'm sorry.

18:51.063 --> 18:52.865
Come here.

18:52.898 --> 18:58.804
(pensive instrumental)

18:58.837 --> 19:03.442
