19:03.475 --> 19:05.777
Mm, I'm sorry you had
to grow up so fast.

19:09.848 --> 19:11.083
Your mother and me, ya-

19:13.085 --> 19:14.653
You took care of both of us.

19:17.890 --> 19:18.891
And, um,

19:19.925 --> 19:22.227
I just don't want you to
have to do that anymore.

19:32.070 --> 19:33.338
Look, Dad, whatever-

19:35.040 --> 19:36.542
Whatever your plan is-

19:44.049 --> 19:46.585
You can't just let Lise
walk out of your life.

20:07.339 --> 20:08.373
You okay?

20:08.407 --> 20:09.641
Yep.

20:10.142 --> 20:11.910
McLeod:
Guys, Kular's got something.

20:12.778 --> 20:15.314
