20:21.787 --> 20:24.189
Rebecca Bailey,
master's student, 26.

20:24.223 --> 20:26.024
Raped and murdered
in the area.

20:26.058 --> 20:28.327
And this is the guy
convicted for it.

20:28.360 --> 20:30.862
Scott Riley, 28 at the time.

20:30.896 --> 20:32.998
Cardinal:
You talked to the
lead investigator?

20:33.031 --> 20:34.600
He died four years ago.

20:34.633 --> 20:36.768
Riley did time at Collins Bay.

20:36.802 --> 20:39.037
His sentence overlapped
with Wade Kleiss.

20:40.472 --> 20:42.174
He got out eight months ago.

20:42.207 --> 20:43.375
We're checking his
prints against the ones

20:43.408 --> 20:44.610
found at the workshop scene.

20:44.643 --> 20:45.978
We have an address for him?

20:46.011 --> 20:47.212
Kular:
Toronto.

20:47.246 --> 20:49.414
After some post-release
time in a halfway house,

20:49.448 --> 20:51.049
he moved into his
late parents' home.

20:51.083 --> 20:52.718
You talk to his P.O.?

20:52.751 --> 20:54.086
Just now.

20:54.119 --> 20:55.520
Riley did an
in-person check in

20:55.554 --> 20:58.056
around the time of Robert
and Adele's murders.

20:58.090 --> 21:00.192
Next one's not scheduled
till tomorrow.

21:00.225 --> 21:01.460
And we think he'd
go back for that?

21:01.493 --> 21:03.095
Try to preserve his alibi?

21:03.128 --> 21:04.529
I think we should
go down there.

21:04.563 --> 21:06.265
Search the house at least.

21:06.298 --> 21:08.133
Rebecca Bailey's
murder case was OPD.

21:08.166 --> 21:10.202
Call Commanda, ask for
everything they have.

