24:42.647 --> 24:44.616
So he quit his job.

24:44.649 --> 24:46.618
Parole Officer:
Started to attend rallies.

24:46.651 --> 24:48.653
Became a bit of a figurehead.

24:48.687 --> 24:50.722
Ended up in some
trouble with the law.

24:50.755 --> 24:52.657
Anything violent?

24:52.691 --> 24:55.093
Parole Officer:
I, I only know what's in his
files and what he told me.

24:55.126 --> 24:56.094
Cardinal:
Hm.

24:56.127 --> 24:57.829
What's he said about
Rebecca Bailey?

24:57.863 --> 24:59.164
That he didn't kill her.

24:59.197 --> 25:00.432
Do you believe him?

25:01.600 --> 25:02.534
I don't know.

25:02.567 --> 25:04.436
I'm just trying to keep
him from going back.

25:04.469 --> 25:06.404
But he must have
spoken about her.

25:06.438 --> 25:11.409
He said he fell in love with
her in the moment he saw her.

25:11.443 --> 25:13.645
They met doing eco work,

25:13.678 --> 25:15.480
uh, pipeline protests,

25:15.514 --> 25:17.315
logging, stuff like that.

25:17.349 --> 25:20.619
He ever say what they were
doing in Algonquin Bay in '99?

25:20.652 --> 25:21.987
Something about birds.

25:22.020 --> 25:23.722
Um, she was an ornithologist.

25:23.755 --> 25:25.824
They heard about
some endangered one

25:25.857 --> 25:29.294
and went up to try and get
its habitat protected.

25:29.327 --> 25:30.729
This bird,

25:30.762 --> 25:32.731
was it a Peregrine Falcon?

25:32.764 --> 25:34.533
I think that's what
he said, yeah.

25:37.936 --> 25:39.170
(elevator dings)

25:40.739 --> 25:44.242
Delorme:
McLeod says Scott Riley's
emptied all his bank accounts.

25:44.276 --> 25:47.546
Cardinal:
Well, he's probably
figuring to go on the run

25:47.579 --> 25:49.147
after all this is over.

25:50.749 --> 25:51.983
Delorme:
Or maybe making sure

25:52.017 --> 25:54.686
he's got everything
he needs to finish.

25:54.719 --> 25:57.923
Cardinal:
Mm, well lab confirms
some of the prints

25:57.956 --> 26:01.493
from the old Cuthberts'
workshop match Riley.

26:02.761 --> 26:05.297
But still no sight of
him in Algonquin Bay.

26:20.145 --> 26:23.915
Um, I'll see you in
the lobby at 5:30?

26:25.650 --> 26:27.152
Yeah, goodnight.

